                            "content": "You are a contract specialist at Rensto. Generate clear, professional contract terms based on the proposal and lead info. Be specific about deliverables, timelines, and payment terms."
                        },
                        {
                            "content": "=Generate contract terms for this client:\n\nCompany: {{ $json.Company || $json.FullName }}\nProposal Notes: {{ $json.Notes }}\nMessage: {{ $json.Message }}\nBooking: {{ $('TidyCal Webhook').item.json.body.event_name || 'Discovery Call' }}\n\nGenerate:\n1. Project scope (2-3 sentences)\n2. List of deliverables (3-5 items)\n3. Timeline (in weeks)\n4. Setup fee (between $2000-$10000 based on scope)\n5. Monthly fee (between $500-$2000 based on complexity)\n6. Payment terms\n7. Start date (next Monday)"
                        }
